---
title: Smokey Chicken & Garlic Crouton Salad with Caramelised Onion & Avocado
description: Tender, smokey chicken pairs perfectly with crunchy garlic croutons in this hearty salad, brought to life with sweet caramelised onions. Finished with a creamy mayo drizzle, every bite offers a satisfying balance of smokey, sweet, and savoury flavors.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/678071c019b5d36400fb18a1-2bab355e.jpeg
